# TachFileTo - BÀN TAY SẮT V1.0 (.gitignore)

# --- CORE ARTIFACTS ---
target/
**/target/
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
dist/
**/dist/
.venv/
.env
.env.*
**/thirdparty/
**/third-party/
**/vendor/
!libs/elite_pdf/vendor/*.lib

# --- COMPILED BINARIES (BLOCKED AT ROOT) ---
*.pyd
*.lib
*.exp
*.pdb
*.exe
*.dll

# --- LOGS & DEBUG SNAPS ---
*.log
*.txt
!README.md
!LESSONS.md
!requirements.txt
check_errors_*.txt
compile_error.log
final_build_log.txt
test_output.txt

# --- DATABASE ---
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

# --- OS/IDE DEBRIS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
temp/
extraction_temp/
*.tmp
*.bak
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bk

# --- EXCEPTIONS ---
!libs/elite_pdf/vendor/*.lib 
